para_trans: Fun, scream. New Primary Health Centre sanctioned at Pavani District Bhandara
Government Decision No: Proceedings-2024 / No.283 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,

Read: Letter from Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries), Mumbai No. A / C / Room-7A / T-5 / Pre-Centre / Establishment / Chichal / Bhandara / 3657-59/2024, D 26/09/2024.
Introduction - Mouje Chichal, Ta. A proposal to sanction a new primary health centre at Pavani District Bhandara was under consideration of the government.
Fun, scream. To sanction a new Primary Health Centre at Pavani District Bhandara.
This Government decision is being approved as a "special case." for this Primary Health Centre.
Separate action will be taken by the Zilla Parishad to acquire the land in the prescribed manner and create the post after completion of the construction.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
